caption.text:
Saya, Jennifer Faustin, percaya bahwa calon dokter di Papua Barat berhak untuk mendapatkan hak belajarnya kembali!
.
Sejak 2 Oktober 2016, kegiatan perkuliahan FK UNIPA terhenti karena ketiadaan dana operasional pendidikan untuk pengampuan. Mahasiswa FK UNIPA telah berupaya untuk meminta solusi dari berbagai pihak pimpinan seperti Rektor UNIPA, DPRD Kabupaten Sorong, DPRD Provinsi Papua Barat, hingga Kementerian Riset, Teknologi, dan Pendidikan Tinggi (Kemenristekdikti). Namun hingga saat ini, belum ada kepastian kapan kegiatan perkuliahan akan kembali stabil.
. 
Walaupun demikian, semangat mereka untuk kembali belajar begitu tinggi. Saya mengajak @blasiusadrian @feliciaangga @anitacarolinatata @debb_van @eirinyovita untuk meneruskan pesan ini dengan gunakan twibbon bit.ly/SaveFKUNIPA dan terus bantu berikan dukungan terbaik dengan mengisi petisi bit.ly/SaveFKUnipa
.
Dengan ini, semoga Papua Barat tidak akan kehilangan 102 calon dokter yang bisa meningkatkan kualitas kesehatan masyarakat disana. #SaveFKUnipa

caption.text:
[WORLD IMMUNIZATION WEEK 2017]

Immunization saves millions of lives and is widely recognized as one of the world’s most successful and cost-effective health interventions. Nowadays there are still 19.4 million unvaccinated and under-vaccinated children in the world. 
So, I Jennifer, am giving my full support to join this celebration to promote the use of vaccines to protect people of all ages against disease. 
I encourage all people of the world to join us in their #VaccinesWork campaign to prevent millions of deaths from vaccine-preventable diseases and raise awareness about the critical importance of full immunization throughout life. 
#VaccinesWork
#BeShield
#VivaAMSA

[WORLD HEALTH DAY 2017]
Depression can be effectively prevented and treated. The cheapest treatment you can get is a talking therapy.
Talking with people you trust can be a first step towards recovery from depression.

Considering that today is the World Health Day, We support this health campaign to fight against Depression by encouraging one another and support each other up, in order to build confidence in living life.

#LetsTalk
#EndDepressionTogether
